# Whisper GGML model cache (downloaded on first run) — anchored to the
# specific runtime project paths so it never matches C# "Models" source
# folders (e.g. VideoSubtitleTranslator.Core/Models), which git on Windows
# would otherwise treat as equivalent due to case-insensitive matching.
